headline: Baird Raises PT on Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) to $600 From $590, Keeps an Overweight Rating
summary: Intuitive Surgical, Inc. (NASDAQ:ISRG) is one of the best stocks to invest in for beginners. On July 24, Baird raised the firm’s price target on Intuitive Surgical, Inc. (NASDAQ:ISRG) to $600 from $590, keeping an Outperform rating on the shares. The firm told investors that the limited share rally after earnings took it by surprise, […]
